    "d0c3aad8-c446-413a-b8c8-d61ddc7f1d33": {
      "id": "d0c3aad8-c446-413a-b8c8-d61ddc7f1d33",
      "node_type": "DataPoint",
      "properties": {
        "content": "Beyond the Hype: Why Generative AI Is Only One Leaf on the AI Tree \n\nMost organisations are pouring resources into Generative AI, but the AI revolution is far broader, and many are overlooking other powerful technologies already shaping the future.\n\nIn 2025, here\u2019s the bigger picture:\n\nRule-based / Expert Systems / Knowledge-based AI \u2013 Hardcoded, deterministic logic. Status: Long-standing, not new.\n\nAnalytical / Predictive / Descriptive / Prescriptive AI \u2013 Forecasting, analytics, and action recommendations. Status: Widespread, works alongside generative.\n\nGenerative AI / Creative AI / Content AI \u2013 Creates text, images, video, and more. Example: ChatGPT, DALL\u00b7E. Status: Widespread.\n\nNeuro-symbolic AI / Hybrid AI / Reasoning AI \u2013 Combines reasoning, logic, and learning. Example: Legal/scientific AI. Status: Emerging, partially post-generative.\n\nAdaptive AI / Continual Learning AI / Self-Optimising AI \u2013 Continuously self-learns in real time. Example: Process control. Status: Emerging, next wave.\n\nAgentic AI / Autonomous AI / Goal-driven AI / AI Agents \u2013 Autonomous, goal-driven agents. Example: AI nurse, AI customer service. Status: Rapidly emerging, next wave.\n\nMulti-modal AI / Foundation Models / General-purpose AI \u2013 Cross-media AI (text, audio, image, video). Example: All-in-one assistants. Status: Post-generative, growth phase.\n\nFederated AI / Edge AI / Privacy-preserving AI \u2013 Privacy-focused, decentralised learning. Status: Expanding alongside current models.\n\nCausal AI / Cause-and-effect AI / Explainable Causal Modelling \u2013 Understands cause-effect relationships. Status: Advanced prototypes, research stage.\n\nNeuromorphic AI / Brain-inspired AI / Quantum AI \u2013 Brain-inspired or quantum-powered AI. Status: Experimental.\n\nSpeculative AI / Artificial General Intelligence (AGI) / Theory-of-Mind AI / Self-aware AI \u2013 Hypothetical future forms. Status: Still conceptual.\n\nIf your AI roadmap stops at Generative AI, you\u2019re optimising for yesterday\u2019s disruption, not tomorrow\u2019s. The organisations that thrive will be the ones preparing for the full AI spectrum now.\n\n#AI #Innovation #FutureOfWork #ArtificialIntelligence #BusinessStrategy #BeyondGenerativeAI #SukhSandhu",
        "source_info": {
          "source": "search.php",
          "timestamp": "2025-09-10T05:49:50.958560",
          "entities": {},
          "follow_up_needed": null,
          "relevance_score": 0.8,
          "goal_relevance_score": 0.5
        },
        "source": "search.php",
        "timestamp": "2025-09-10T05:49:50.958560"
